    <div class="grid-row">

      <div class="column-two-thirds">

        <h1 class="heading-xlarge">{{{title}}}</h1>

        <div class="panel  panel-border-narrow">
          <p>This is your opportunity to respond to the court.</p>
          <ul class="list list-bullet">
            <li>the charge details and witness statements are in the documentation sent to you</li>
            <li>each offence may carry a fine</li>
            <li>if you plead guilty you may get a reduction on any fine imposed</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <hr class="divider  divider-gutter-large" aria-hidden="true">

