        <h2 class="heading-large">Enter your plea</h2>

        <form class="form" method="post">

          <div class="form-group">

            <fieldset class="inline">

              <legend>
                <span class="form-label-bold">How do you plead?</span>
              </legend>

              <label class="block-label  selection-button-radio" data-target="pleadGuilty">
                <input type="radio" name="howDoYouPlead" value="Guilty"><span class="visually-hidden"> I plead</span> Guilty
              </label>

              <label class="block-label  selection-button-radio" data-target="pleadNotGuilty">
                <input type="radio" name="howDoYouPlead" value="Not guilty"><span class="visually-hidden"> I plead</span> Not guilty
              </label>

            </fieldset>

            <!-- Guilty -->
            <div class="panel  panel-border-narrow  js-hidden" id="pleadGuilty">

              <p>Pleading <strong>guilty</strong> is an admission that you commited the offence and will be convicted and sentanced based on the submission of your guilty plea.</p>

              <p>You have three options for how you can plead guilty to this offence:</p>

              <div class="form-group">

                <fieldset class="inline">

                  <legend class="visually-hidden">How do you plead guilty to this offence?</legend>

                  <div class="form-group  form-group-compound">
                    <label class="block-label selection-button-radio">
                      <input type="radio" name="howDoYouPleadGuiltyToThisOffence" value="Accept an automated standard penalty"> Accept an automated standard penalty
                    </label>
                  </div>

                  <div class="form-group  form-group-compound">
                    <label class="block-label selection-button-radio">
                      <input type="radio" name="howDoYouPleadGuiltyToThisOffence" value="Plead guilty (no need to attend court)"> Plead guilty (no need to attend court)
                    </label>
                  </div>

                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="block-label  selection-button-radio">
                      <input type="radio" name="howDoYouPleadGuiltyToThisOffence" value="Attend court to plead guilty"> Attend court to plead guilty
                    </label>
                  </div>

                </fieldset>

              </div>

            </div>

          </div>

          <div class="form-group  form-group-related">
            <button class="button" type="submit">Save and continue</button>
          </div>

          <p><a href="/your-details">Back</a></p>

        </form>

      </div>

    </div>
